37327>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37327>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37328>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37329>>>    End_Procedure
37330>>>    
37330>>>End_Object
